      <title>欧盟不顾法国反对，达成期待已久的南方共同市场协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/eu-reaches-long-sought-mercosur-deal-over-macron-s-objections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管法国强烈反对，欧盟与南美洲南方共同市场仍达成了一项期待已久的贸易协议，法国还誓言将带头阻挠该协议的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/eu-reaches-long-sought-mercosur-deal-over-macron-s-objections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 12:54:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
